---
// src/components/sections/FinalTakeaway.astro
---
<section class="py-12 relative overflow-hidden bg-[#fafafa]">
  <!-- Subtle Background Glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-indigo-100/40 rounded-full blur-[100px] -z-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Compact Card -->
    <div class="group relative bg-white border border-slate-100 rounded-[32px] p-8 md:p-12 text-center shadow-sm transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-indigo-500/5">
      
      <!-- Minimal Header -->
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 bg-indigo-50 rounded-full mb-6">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="text-indigo-600 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Final Thought</span>
      </div>

      <div class="text-slate-500 text-base md:text-lg space-y-6 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto relative z-10">
          <p>
            Journaling is about building a <span class="text-slate-800 font-semibold">relationship with yourself</span>. It’s one of the most reliable resources you will ever have.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            You don't need a perfect plan. You just need the <span class="italic text-slate-600">honesty to show up</span> and have a conversation that no one else can have for you.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Compact Action Box -->
          <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-indigo-50 group-hover:border-indigo-100">
            <p class="text-slate-900 font-bold text-lg leading-tight">
              Pick one technique. <span class="text-indigo-600">Write three sentences.</span> <br class="hidden md:block" /> 
              Start tomorrow and see what happens.
            </p>
          </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>